  "body": "<p>How is it already Friday again?</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5e8815f1adf19b2d.jpg?v=1782530148\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>1. Love this quote that <a href=\"http://ink361.com/app/photo/ig-573933974525409799_476885\">Margie posted on Instagram</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2b668c26bd808f30.jpg?v=1782530151\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>2. So thankful for our happy little guy. He's already 5 weeks old. Oh and to get this shot I stood on our bed and took about 15 shots while he was dancing and cooing up a storm.</p><p>3. We're working a killer Halloween party in Beverly Hills this evening. Last year I staffed the crafters for this mega event with over 700 guests, but I was in Brazil. This year there will be over 900 guests and I get to be there. But there won't be any photos allowed - sorry! We'll be doing jewelry making, hat making and perfume mixing.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/66cb85c063b51be5.jpg?v=1782530154\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>4. JC sent me <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MattBloomFilms/status/388955618876608513/photo/1\">this tweet</a> because he knew I would appreciate it. And I guess we are doing this parenting thing wrong ;)</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5b7bc945d19db8fa.jpg?v=1782530157\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>5. Skipping 5 is hosting a giveaway and discount code!</p><p>Check out all their products and use code \"AMY15\" for 15% off all items including the new colorful heart geotag puffy stickers and screen printed fabric journaling cards. As always, flat rate shipping is $2 for domestic orders and $5 for International. They are also offering custom screen printed journaling cards and flair as well. <strong>GIVEAWAY is closed</strong>:<strong> Leave a comment letting us know what you love or what custom items you'd create! </strong>2 winners will be chosen on Monday, October 28th after 7am and announced on this post. Good luck and have a wonderful weekend!</p><p>Winners are #27 &amp; #44 - Congrats Eri &amp; Nicole McNamara!!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
